QuestDescription.SourceString: Help Vannaka safeguard Fellhollow's nature spirits, by hunting them down, in willow groves, and collecting their hearts.

Value.SourceString: Hunt down Nature Spirits near Fellhollow's willow groves and bring three of their hearts to Vannaka.
